                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-red-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6">
                        🔄
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">
                        Interactive Reflection
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        AI와 함께하는 체계적 복기. 자료구조 상태 추적, 패턴 일반화, 실수 포인트 분석.
                    </p>
                    <a href="#" class="text-orange-600 font-semibold inline-flex items-center hover:text-orange-700">
                        Learn more →
                    </a>
                </div>

                <!-- Feature 5 -->
                <div class="feature-card bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6">
                        🤖
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">
                        Agent Workflows
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Skills로 통합된 학습 세션 자동화. 추천→힌트→풀이→복기 전체 플로우 관리.
                    </p>
                    <a href="#" class="text-cyan-600 font-semibold inline-flex items-center hover:text-cyan-700">
                        Learn more →
                    </a>
                </div>

                <!-- Feature 6 -->
                <div class="feature-card bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-indigo-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6">
                        ⚙️
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">
                        Multi-Platform Support
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        백준(BOJ) ✅ 프로그래머스 🔜 LeetCode 🔜<br>
                        Claude Code, Copilot CLI 지원.
                    </p>
                    <a href="#" class="text-indigo-600 font-semibold inline-flex items-center hover:text-indigo-700">
                        Learn more →
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works -->
    <section id="how-it-works" class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 via-purple-50 to-pink-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-purple-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">How It Works</h2>
                <p class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                    Get started in 3 simple steps
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
                <!-- Step 1 -->
                <div class="text-center fade-in">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl font-bold mx-auto mb-6 shadow-xl">
                        1
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Install CoteKit</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        npm install 한 줄로 MCP 서버와 Skills 설치. 30초면 완료됩니다.
                    </p>
                    <div class="glass p-4 rounded-xl text-left">
                        <code class="text-sm text-gray-700">
                            $ npm install -g @cotekit/mcp-server
                        </code>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 2 -->
                <div class="text-center fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl font-bold mx-auto mb-6 shadow-xl">
                        2
                    </div>
