                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        Claude Code 또는 GitHub Copilot CLI에 CoteKit 연동. 자동 설정 스크립트 제공.
                    </p>
                    <div class="glass p-4 rounded-xl text-left">
                        <code class="text-sm text-gray-700">
                            $ cote-kit configure claude
                        </code>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 3 -->
                <div class="text-center fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-teal-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl font-bold mx-auto mb-6 shadow-xl">
                        3
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Start Learning</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        /cote:session 명령으로 학습 시작. 문제 추천부터 복기까지 자동화됩니다.
                    </p>
                    <div class="glass p-4 rounded-xl text-left">
                        <code class="text-sm text-gray-700">
                            You: /cote:session 1003
                        </code>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Philosophy / USP -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-6xl mb-8">🧠</div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                Learning Philosophy
            </h2>
            <blockquote class="text-3xl text-blue-600 font-bold mb-8 italic">
                "Learn by thinking, not by seeing answers"
            </blockquote>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
                CoteKit은 답을 주지 않습니다. 대신 <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">생각하는 법</span>을 안내합니다.
                프롬프트 기반 아키텍처로 문제마다 맞춤형 힌트를 제공하여, 스스로 해결할 수 있도록 돕습니다.
            </p>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-12">
                <div class="glass p-8 rounded-2xl">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🧠</div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Level 1</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">문제 접근법<br><span class="text-sm italic text-gray-500">(What to think)</span></p>
                </div>
                <div class="glass p-8 rounded-2xl">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🛠️</div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Level 2</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">구현 힌트<br><span class="text-sm italic text-gray-500">(How to implement)</span></p>
                </div>
                <div class="glass p-8 rounded-2xl">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-4">✅</div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Level 3</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">정답 검증<br><span class="text-sm italic text-gray-500">(Verify solution)</span></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing (Simple) -->
    <section id="pricing" class="py-24 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-green-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Pricing</h2>
                <p class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                    Simple, transparent pricing
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
                <!-- Free Tier -->
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-gray-200">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Free</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">For students and learners</p>
                    <div class="mb-6">
                        <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900">$0</span>
                        <span class="text-gray-600">/month</span>
                    </div>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                            </svg>
                            <span class="text-gray-600">Basic problem recommendations</span>
